node_modules/
dist/
*.tsbuildinfo
coverage/
.DS_Store
*.log
# ADR 058: the durable seat roster (.musterd/team.toml + seats/) is committed; only the
# secret-bearing binding token is ignored — in any folder (** covers root + nested).
**/.musterd/binding.json
# ADR 080's committed launch spec is a *downstream-repo* feature (a fresh clone self-wires from it).
# In musterd's OWN dogfood repo it's per-worktree launch config (team + seat) that every agent
# re-stamps to its own identity — a perpetual uncommitted drift — so we ignore it here. The self-wire
# feature is unaffected (it lives in CLI code; a user repo still `git add`s its own workspace.json).
**/.musterd/workspace.json
# ADR 033: client-side pending-presence markers are transient local state, never committed.
**/.musterd/pending/
*.db
*.db-wal
*.db-shm

# secret-bearing harness configs (security.md operational guidance)
.cursor/mcp.json

# Qoder editor workspace state — local tooling, never committed
.qoder/

.env
